    Topology.P1 (interior A) âˆ§ Topology.P3 (interior A) := by

    simpa using (interior_has_P2 (X := X) (A := A))
  have hP1 : Topology.P1 (interior A) := (P2_implies_P1 (X := X) (A := interior A)) hP2

  exact And.intro hP1 hP3
